dc_title_s: Hydro (Line and Polygon) Washington County, WI 2024
dc_description_s: This data represents hydrography for Washington County, Wisconsin in 2024. The following features are included: 'WASHINGTON_HYDRO_2024_LINE' and 'WASHINGTON_HYDRO_2024_POLY'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://maps.washcowisco.gov/portal/apps/sites/#/maps
